  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-05 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A mesh-sensitivity verification activity is declared but no evidence in this package references that activity as its provenance source, creating an activity-evidence consistency gap (W-CON-05).",
