    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels. Six factors were flagged as not assessed due to epistemic gaps. The mesh sensitivity verification activity was declared and is referenced in the factor rationale, but the corresponding evidence artefact has not been linked in this package. Despite these deficiencies, the assessment package is accepted for submission pending evidence linkage in a subsequent revision.",
